   1:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp **** /**
   2:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   * @file    My_HID_Keyboard.c
   3:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   * @brief   AL94 USB Composite HID Keyboard 封装层实现
   4:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   * @note    使用 AL94 库原始 HID_KEYBOARD 描述符格式（含 Report ID）
   5:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   *
   6:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   * 描述符格式回顾：
   7:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   *   byte0: Report ID = 0x01（AL94 描述符中 0x85,0x01 定义）
   8:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   *   byte1: Modifier（Ctrl/Shift/Alt/Win 组合键位图）
   9:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   *   byte2: Reserved（保留，固定为 0x00）
  10:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   *   byte3: Keycode1（HID Usage ID）
  11:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   *   byte4: Keycode2
  12:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   *   byte5: Keycode3
  13:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   *   byte6: Keycode4
  14:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   *   byte7: Keycode5
  15:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   *
  16:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   * 数据长度：8 字节
  17:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   *
  18:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   * 重要：
  19:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   *   - 发送前需确保 USB 设备已枚举完成（dev_state == USBD_STATE_CONFIGURED）
  20:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   *   - 每个按键必须发"按下+释放"，否则主机会认为该键一直被按住
  21:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   *   - 按键之间需保持至少 10ms 间隔，给主机轮询时间
  22:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp ****   */
  23:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp **** 
  24:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp **** #include "My_HID_Keyboard.hpp"
  25:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp **** #include "usbd_hid_keyboard.h"
  26:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp **** #include "FreeRTOS.h"
  27:My_Top/USB_Composite/My_HID_Keyboard.cpp **** #include "task.h"
